    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1864-10-25T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1864-10-25T00:00:00-05:00" n="544"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d544">
                <head>
                    <persName type="from">Mr. Seward</persName> to <persName type="to">Mr.
                        Burnley</persName>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State,</hi>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington,</hi>
                        </placeName>
                        <date calendar="gregorian" when="1864-10-25">
                            <hi rend="italic">October</hi> 25, 1864.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir:</hi> I have the honor to acknowledge the receipt of
                    your communication of the 20th instant, relative to the alleged capture of the
                    Night Hawk, and the detention of her crew as prisoners; and, in reply, to inform
                    you that I have transmitted a copy thereof to the Secretary of the Navy, who has
                    been requested to investigate the case, with a view to the adoption of such
                    proceedings as the result may call for.</p>
                <p>Accept, sir, a renewed assurance of my high consideration,</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>WILLIAM H. SEWARD.</signed>
                </closer>
                <postscript>
                    <p>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">J. Hume Burnley,</hi> Esq., <hi rend="italic">&amp;c.,
                            &amp;c., &amp;c.</hi>
                    </p>
                </postscript>
            </div>
        </body>
